snippet.title: Even Her Mechanic Hates Her | Johnny depp's ex-wife Vanessa Paradis calls out Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny depp's ex-wife Vanessa Paradis calls out Amber Heard | Even Her Mechanic Hates Her

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________

Johnny Depp's ex-partner Vanessa Paradis has made statements saying the star was never vioIent towards her. She has described Johnny Depp as a 'kind, attentive, generous and non-vioIent person and father', according to court documents in his libel claim. His ex lover Winona Ryder has also said she "cannot wrap her head around" allegations of abuse against him.
